{"tid":1680062,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［香城online］新職業-星之子","createTime":"2019-10-28T14:40:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-28T14:48:08.000Z","uid":312550,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"acb7c09efe94fa7bdf1a9998e8034432904ac67d","tid":1680062,"uid":312550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T14:40:23.000Z","msg":"和理非又可以玩多項職業喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n新職業：<span style=\"color: blue;\">星之子</span><br />\n需要器材：<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">觀星筆</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">工具十分易得！！！喺過去4個月，相信唔少手足都有觀身筆㗎啦</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n依家狗狗係唔係就出直升機，佢哋有制高點睇到手足行動其實係好不利嘅，琴日見到咁多手足被拉就知<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ULpAC7J.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FULpAC7J.png&h=18b0b920&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n借一借ching嘅po先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁依家只需要街坊同和理非一人一支觀星筆觀星，當然都可以多過一支啦，<span style=\"color: blue;\">一齊睇星星</span>，就可以救到前線手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過千其千其唔好唔小心<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">射中玩緊直升機嘅狗狗呀</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n約多啲人一齊睇星星啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同我快啲推到比多啲人見到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"93d55eb065bcd6a0368b063183ca6639c77fea7a","tid":1680062,"uid":312550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T14:41:03.000Z","msg":"P牌自推"},{"pid":"fadc85518960c0c3d3ce93e217a7771f4b18e28a","tid":1680062,"uid":200733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T14:41:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DqJJM98.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDqJJM98.jpg&h=3b84c598&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1467be8782598245f29184a3354d931c55e570a9","tid":1680062,"uid":312550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T14:42:12.000Z","msg":"P牌自推十連"},{"pid":"06a74a16fda1c25d08918061aeb176863c83d491","tid":1680062,"uid":312550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T14:42:58.000Z","msg":"一連"},{"pid":"7ae1dba43b232579002135d99dd610eaa4571ee0","tid":1680062,"uid":312550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T14:43:47.000Z","msg":"二連"},{"pid":"71fc37155851b794e8ec84382855c434e6b8fa01","tid":1680062,"uid":312550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T14:45:01.000Z","msg":"三連"},{"pid":"18969dd418dc85c83f73d4fa2b1722abf6669b67","tid":1680062,"uid":312550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T14:45:28.000Z","msg":"四連"},{"pid":"01d6932f857509d6ce771954786b64299e521f78","tid":1680062,"uid":312550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T14:45:42.000Z","msg":"五連"},{"pid":"74f9c8df73d6fc2aecef1421e402e769fa8c3697","tid":1680062,"uid":312550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T14:46:36.000Z","msg":"六連"},{"pid":"43a9337428ededbdd39df24bc784cb3bbffc6b09","tid":1680062,"uid":312550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T14:46:50.000Z","msg":"七連"},{"pid":"615f8c26fb27376a7f4d5a08dc9ed8508fa61701","tid":1680062,"uid":312550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T14:47:25.000Z","msg":"八連"},{"pid":"c90ea00ac3fdb5ba81434a834422dd91d80bd597","tid":1680062,"uid":312550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T14:47:58.000Z","msg":"九連"},{"pid":"4f5a81ab57a0f2b3721ae297745bea5d6b24eacd","tid":1680062,"uid":312550,"like":0,"dislik